text: Theodosis Kyprou (; born 24 February 1992 in Cyprus) is a Cypriot football Forward who is currently playing for Ermis Aradippou. ==Career== He made his first appearance for Omonia against Paphos and he was in the starting line-up against Apollon Limassol for first time. ==Honours== Omonia *Cypriot Championship: 2010 *Cypriot Cup: 2011 *Cyprus FA Shield: 2010 ==External links== * *UEFA profile Category:Living people Category:1992 births Category:Sportspeople from Nicosia Category:Greek Cypriot people Category:Cypriot footballers Category:Cypriot expatriate footballers Category:Cyprus under-21 international footballers Category:Association football forwards Category:AC Omonia players Category:Chalkanoras Idaliou players Category:Aris Limassol FC players Category:AEL Kalloni F.C. players Category:Ermis Aradippou FC players Category:Super League Greece players Category:Cypriot First Division players Category:Cypriot Second Division players Category:Cypriot expatriate sportspeople in Greece Category:Expatriate footballers in Greece
